{"tid":2060672,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 我就是極少數，想尋求法律意見。","createTime":"2020-06-11T23:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T00:42:28.000Z","uid":116630,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8666821c4f21e0d0ae2988835f6608867ac17b22","tid":2060672,"uid":116630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:37:05.000Z","msg":"之前，和理非有好多種的抗議手法。 我覺得而家呢個時候，係時候番來啦。 我想大家諗諗計，睇下點樣將個標題的意念發揚光大。 話比全世界知， 香港有好多的&quot;極少數&quot;. 他們可能是屋邨仔， 可以係二世祖，甚至可以係就死既阿伯。 個message 最重要的地方，是貼地，講下你本人如何成為了&quot;極少數&quot;。 <br />\n<br />\nexample: 我是一個普通的和理非， 只是參加過民陣的各類遊行， 一出催淚彈就會離開。 我一向都無諗過成為&quot;極少數&quot;, 但是，當北京推出國安法，令我覺得香港已經再沒出路，因此，我現在成為了&quot;極少數&quot;. 作為&quot;極少數&quot; 新人，我想尋求法律支援，我是否要去警處自首？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsorry ,1999."},{"pid":"92051eaef28c8cf04f22bcde728a13b257e0a46a","tid":2060672,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:38:04.000Z","msg":"套料？屌你老母。"},{"pid":"c17b5b845d9405b4c05eb71c3629ea2fd0987741","tid":2060672,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:42:14.000Z","msg":"國際線"},{"pid":"e13010cc1997515cb5948b14b632b402da7d94d9","tid":2060672,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92051eaef28c8cf04f22bcde728a13b257e0a46a","tid":2060672,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:38:04.000Z","msg":"套料？屌你老母。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7792fd4df3007546318ec6766349cd5fb19c96a6","tid":2060672,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:52:32.000Z","msg":"up乜野"},{"pid":"0a1b3c37584c389783501f0f3703edf0d34b8a13","tid":2060672,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:53:35.000Z","msg":"i don't know what 7 you say"},{"pid":"a35e662e96d086a0a08d05f10503c334b37b8ac3","tid":2060672,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0